## Learn


### Working with Forms
* Form UI
* Action Page
* Reading Data


### Form UI
Define a target page for receiving data

```
<form action="send_email.php" method="POST">
```



### Input Fields
Define controls to gather data

```
<input type="text" name="phone_number">
```



### Submit Button
Define a button to send the form data

```
<input type="submit" value="Save">
```



### Pushing Submit Button
* Invokes the "method" on the "action" page
* eg. Do a POST operation on "send_email.php"


### Collecting Data
* filter_input - Extracts one value from the Request

```
$name = filter_input(INPUT_POST, 'my_name');
```



### Validating Email
* Optional code can check for certain conditions



```
$name = filter_input(INPUT_POST, 'email', FILTER_VALIDATE_EMAIL);
```



